You are here:
Watch CRM Analytics Learning Days Webinars
Learn directly from expert trainers. The Learning Days webinars cover a range of topics on CRM Analytics and Einstein Discovery, with deep dives into use cases, common questions, and best practices to inspire and guide you to create great analytics implementations.

CRM Analytics Learning Days - Best Practices
This series presents best practices for designing solutions in CRM Analytics.

CRM Analytics Learning Days - Prepare and Integrate Data
This series has webinars on data preparation and data integration.

CRM Analytics Learning Days - Build and Produce Dashboards
This series presents processes to follow for creating effective dashboards.

CRM Analytics Learning Days - Add Intelligence
This series has webinars on Einstein Discovery and AI in CRM Analytics.

CRM Analytics Learning Days - Extend Dashboard Functionality
This series includes webinars on advanced dashboard design, features, and use cases.

CRM Analytics Learning Days - Thought Leadership
This series features presentations with insights and guidance about analytics in general.
